          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "/By authors/ The cross sections for 20-45 MeV He3 and",
                "alpha and the corresponding reactions-",
                "Cu-65(He3,2n+p)30-Zn-65 and Cu-63(alpha,n+p)30-Zn-65.",
                "have been accurately measured.",
                "/By authors/ Cyclotron production of Xe-123 from",
                "isotopically enriched tellurium targets was evaluated",
                "as a source of high purity I-123 for",
                "radiopharmaceutical applications.",
                "The Te-123(He3,3n)Xe-123 and the Te-124(He3,4n)Xe-123",
                "nuclear reactions have cross sections peaks of 178 mb",
                "and 162 mb at 26 MeV and 45 MeV, respectively.",
                "The Xe-123 thick target production yields for the",
                "reactions were 6.44 mci/muAhr and 7.16 mCi/muAhr",
                "respectively, as compared to large 5 mCi/muAhr for",
                "the Te-122(a,3n)Xe-123 reaction."
              ]
            }
          ],
